<text>
  <chapter>Paṭṭhānappakaraṇa-aṭṭhakathā</chapter>
  <gatha type="1">Devātidevo  devānaṃ, devadānavapūjito,</gatha>
  <gatha type="last">Desayitvā pakaraṇaṃ, yamakaṃ suddhasaṃyamo.</gatha>
  <gatha type="1">Atthato dhammato ceva, gambhīrassātha tassa yaṃ,</gatha>
  <gatha type="last">Anantaraṃ mahāvīro, sattamaṃ isisattamo.</gatha>
  <gatha type="1">Paṭṭhānaṃ nāma nāmena, nāmarūpanirodhano,</gatha>
  <gatha type="last">Desesi atigambhīra-nayamaṇḍitadesanaṃ.</gatha>
  <gatha type="1">Idāni  tassa sampatto, yasmā saṃvaṇṇanākkamo,</gatha>
  <gatha type="last">Tasmā naṃ vaṇṇayissāmi, taṃ suṇātha samāhitāti.</gatha>
</text>
